Types

WaveWrite = ref object
  fileName: string
  riffChunkDescriptor: RIFFChunkDescriptor
  formatSubChunk: FormatSubChunk
  dataSubChunk: DataSubChunk
WaveWrite is a Wave object of fmWrite mode. WaveWrite doesn't have a reading functions.
